<br>
I have decided to organize a few raids.  After all, we cannot leave all the fun to Sirdo and Raaker, can we?<br>
<br>
I have been on a Sirdo raid, and a Raaker raid, and both are extremely organized.  I only hope that I can live up to their leadership abilities.<br>
<br>
I do, however, plan to run my raids slightly differently.  I will have two types.  Quality and quantity.<br>
<br>
Quality - A short to medium length raid to aquire a specific item or items for each member of the raiding force.  IE Umbral Plains to get Moktor gear for the plate wearers, and elysian for the druids, etc.  Once all the items are gotten, the raid is officially over.<br>
<br>
Quantity - A long to extremely long raid spanning an entire day plus.  Raid force will come and go throughout the day, and the items gotten will be randomed and sold in bazaar.  This is mainly a cash raid.  IE Gems, spells, quest items.  This raid does not end until the raiding force can no longer hold a camp.<br>
<br>
I will plan a single raid for each week starting in 3 weeks.  I will list the character requirements(1 war 2 clr) etc.  On the given raid day, we will see who we have, and choose the preplanned raid from there.  That ensures that a raid does not fizzle before it begins.  We just change the raid venue.<br>
<br>
These are the places I have in mind.<br>
Cazic Thule<br>
The Hole<br>
Chardok<br>
Velketor's Labrynth<br>
Umbral Plains<br>
Crypt of Nadox<br>
Plane of Fear<br>
Plane of Hate<br>
Plane of Mischief<br>
<br>
I have some pretty powerful places listed here, but when you<br>
consider the number of people in the guild, and in the alliance who are powerful, it does not seem that difficult.<br>
<br>
I will post a plan of attack for each place, adding in what classes are needed.  If you are not listed in the &quot;needed&quot; part, you are gravy.  That is a good thing.  <br>
<br>
If you have an item that you want, post it here, and I will plan a raid for that.  IE if you need something from fear, we might as well get the epic pieces from there as well, and some armor, etc.<br>
<br>
For obvious reasons, I left out the power raids.  Veeshan, Ssra, ToV, Sleepers.<br>
<br>
While we can be some day, we are not yet powerful enough.  And some of us lack the experience.<br>
<br>
Anyway, I will post the raids in a day or so.<br>
<br>
Damascus Meridias <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub37.ezboard.com/bchivalrousvalor.showUserPublicProfile?gid=destrea>Destrea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Diplomatic Advisor
